description:
Hello, I'm Agatha :)

I love putting on makeup and filming it so here's a video of me creating a masquerade mask look. I just want to document the process of how I made this look and maybe some of you want to do it as well that's why I'm uploading it here on my youtube channel. 

If you do have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them (try ko talaga promise) 

Follow me on instagram @agathaclmn and my makeup portfolio @agatha.hmua

Thanks for watching!
